<A>__{david, jenny, danny and helen in a row in the middle of the auditorium, watching the stage and listening to the music. jenny can't concentrate she's too excited by the occasion and the company. jenny sneaks a glance at helen, who stares straight ahead, unblinking and enigmatic. david is smiling, as if he's trying to communicate enjoyment; danny's eyes flicker across the stage he understands the music, its component parts, which musicians are contributing what. jenny takes it all in.}
